works.description: Design company 2eleven, has chopped a beautiful wooden version of its multimedia foosball table for the eco geeks. The ‘2eleven natural’ is a luxurious German design that boasts built-in extendable cup holders, ergonomically formed grips, leather surfaces, LED displays on either sides, an automatic ball lift to catapult the ball into the middle of the playing field similar to slingshot of a pin-ball machine, aluminum-made counter and a score display with beautiful craftsmanship and elegant make. The players are made of solid maple and walnut. The legs feature an intricate tread profile for stability
